description: - Air quality data (2018-2024): Pre-generated data from EPA (United States Environmental Protection Agency).<https://aqs.epa.gov/aqsweb/airdata/download_files.html> - Fine resolution AQ data: Air Quality System (AQS) API <https://aqs.epa.gov/aqsweb/documents/data_api.html> - COPD data: National Environmental Public Health Tracking Network <https://ephtracking.cdc.gov/DataExplorer/> - Demographic data: Census data from the Office for National Statistics. <https://www.ons.gov.uk/census>
